Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 22:01:26 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 6/8] fix(windows): enable native system notifications

Replace the Windows Ok(false) stub with a Shell_NotifyIconW notification-area
icon and informational balloon. Allocate a distinct icon ID per notification,
truncate UTF-16 fields without splitting surrogate pairs, and remove the
temporary icon after the balloon has had time to display.

Keep notification audio policy separate: NIIF_NOSOUND prevents an additional
shell sound, and this patch does not change src/sound.rs.

refs #1330

Extracted from c340f9c53c9d512ce0da5652cf3389dcb66b3c33 and
7317b303f4599b66ea56f41ff1e0912a91b1549f.
